name: NounPunks
description:
NounPunks is a group of 9969 beings
inspired by the world of LarvaLabs and SuperGremplin
that bridges the autonomy of separate cultures
forming the first hybrid culture with a FU attitude
that !vibes in the fabric of block and time.
No roadmap, no utility, just !vibe   

This project is in the public domain. Feel free to use NounPunks in any way you want.
